author: Kyle Olson, Kyle Olson
title: Joe Biden Mistakenly Calls Coronavirus the 'Luhan Virus'
description: Democrat presidential front runner Joe Biden called the coronavirus by the wrong name again during a virtual town hall on Friday.
content:
Democrat presidential front runner Joe Biden called the coronavirus by the wrong name again during a virtual town hall on Friday.
